data.description: ****ASSUMABLE LOAN WITH A 2.875% INTEREST RATE **  Come check out this cute 2 bed 2 bath A-Frame home in the city limits of Texarkana, Tx..    Kitchen was previously remodeled and has a stainless Farm sink. Dining area has a large pantry for extra storage. Move upstairs to find a bed and bath with a small sitting, Tv, or study area for the kids. Upstairs also has a small balcony off the bedroom.  Fenced in back yard, with a large storage building on approx. half an acre.
